\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ytr1665703174503.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ytr1665703174503.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ytr1665703174503.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ytr1665703174503\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Provide authentication information. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ytr1665703174503__section_w3718ab1b5b1_w3719ab1b5_w3720ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d164097e49\">Return Values</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"ytr1665703174503__parml_opb_pg1_fwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">USEC_SUCCESS</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Authentication successful, no info returned  </dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">USEC_INFO</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Authentication successful, info returned in Error members </dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">USEC_ERROR</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Authentication failed, error returned in Error members </dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ytr1665703174503__section_w3721ab1b5b3_w3722ab1b5_w3723ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d164097e85\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ytr1665703174503__p_d132389e1_d132390e1_d132391e1\">Provide authentication information, such as ‘Your\n        password will expire in <var class=\"keyword varname\">x</var> days’, and so forth. The username is a\n        null-terminated string in <code class=\"ph codeph\">Username</code>. The password is a null-terminated\n        string in <code class=\"ph codeph\">Passwd</code>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534262\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534262\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "USEC_USERPASSINFO Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 15, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Provide authentication information. Return Values USEC_SUCCESS Authentication successful, no info returned USEC_INFO Authentication successful, info returned in Error members USEC_ERROR Authentication failed, error returned in Error members Description Provide authentication information, such as ‘Your password will expire in x days’, and so forth. The username is a null-terminated string in Username . The password is a null-terminated string in Passwd . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}